{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">掌握碳酸钠溶液与澄清石灰水反应的原理。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Na<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3&nbsp;</sub>+ Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub>&nbsp;= 2NaOH + CaCO<sub>3</sub>&darr;</span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：试管、胶头滴管。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：碳酸钠溶液、氢氧化钙溶液。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在试管中加入少量氢氧化钙溶液，然后滴加碳酸钠溶液，观察实验现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">产生白色沉淀。</span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}